text:
Foo Fighters joined James Corden in the latest Carpool Karaoke!

The rockers and The Late Late Show host drove to a guitar store and even put on an impromptu concert in the store covering Rick Astley's "Never Gonna Give You Up."
title: Foo Fighters & James Corden Cover "Never Gonna Give You Up" In Guitar Store
